Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:15.57,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}It's hard to be a normal person, that's just not me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:20.87,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I'm writing a journal to keep my feelings hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.50,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}I cross the bridge what would I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:26.33,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Wanna see it dreamin' my dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.09,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Miracles, beautiful Here we go, all the way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:32.51,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Running from my life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.05,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}It's no use to keep holding back my thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:36.51,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}It would be wrong if you're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.30,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Found my way through the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:41.77,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}If I could reach to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.77,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Money still can't buy me love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.35,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}There's still life when there's hope around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:51.15,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Like a rainbow in the clouds, a gift from above
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:57.24,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Kiss me before the sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:01:03.25,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Or I'm leaving you tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:08.04,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Knowing I've found a place to stay and rest, it's like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:13.67,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Always stayin' forever, meant to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.76,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}If we could change this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:20.43,OPEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}Today with you
